Description:
We are currently hiring a Junior/Mid/Senior Data Analyst who will be responsible for:
Building and maintaining key reports/dashboards to monitor business performance;
Owning advanced end-to-end analyses, from extracting data to analyzing and presenting insights, to answer important business questions;
Together with the Data Engineer team, ensuring a high level of data quality to serve as the source of truth for the whole organization;
Participating in the product development process by consulting product and IT teams with relevant metrics and data requirements;
Using data to identify opportunities for improvement to enable functional departments to achieve operational excellence.

Required:
At least 01 year of experience in Data Analyst or Business Analyst or Business Intelligence;
Good understanding of different business processes (product development, sales & marketing, business strategies) as well as database concepts and common data flows within an organization;
Proficient SQL required. Other programming languages such as Python, R are preferred;
Knowledge of statistical techniques and concepts such as regression, statistical distributions, statistical tests is preferred;
Experience with visualization tools such as Tableau, Google Data Studio, PowerBI;
Ability to give clear and actionable recommendations based on data findings;
Strong critical/logical thinking;
Good English skills is a big plus.

Benifits:
Salary + lunch allowance;
13th month salary + performance bonus;
100% salary during probation period (02 months);
Bao Viet Insurance;
Macbook provided (upon the positions);
Support leadership & technical training courses;
Social insurance base on company policy & labor law;
Yearly business trip;
Gift for birthday and holidays;
Teambuilding, company trips, internal event...
Flexible working hours, from Mondays to Fridays.

Required:
- Tốt nghiệp Đại học các ngành liên quan đến lĩnh vực Công nghệ thông tin; Hệ thống thông tin; QTKD. Tiếng Anh giao tiếp tốt; Sử dụng thành thạo vi tính văn phòng;
- Tối thiểu 02 năm kinh nghiệm trong lĩnh vực phân phối hàng hóa, sản phẩm (bao gồm cả triển khai và vận hành hệ thống);
- Kỹ năng tổ chức, quản lý và làm việc nhóm. Tinh thần, trách nhiệm và có khả năng làm việc dưới môi trường nhiều áp lực, liên tục thay đổi. Có khả năng đi công tác thường xuyên.

Benifits:
- Ứng viên trúng tuyển sẽ làm việc tại TP.Hồ Chí Minh;
- Được làm việc trong môi trường năng động, chuyên nghiệp, có nhiều cơ hội thăng tiến;
